text: Ishemgul () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Novochebenkinsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 671 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Ishemgul
